SIMPLE: unexpressive
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unexpressive
<hw>Un`ex*press"ive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Not expressive; not having the power of utterance;
inexpressive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Incapable of being expressed; inexpressible;
unutterable; ineffable.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Run, run, Orlando; carve on every tree⟦br⟧
The fair, the chaste and <qex>unexpressive</qex> she.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un`ex*press"ive*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unextinguishable</ent>⟦br⟧
